<div id="content">        <div class="spacer"></div>             <span id="shash-22747"><div class="post" id="post-22747">                    <h1><a href="http://trilema.com/2011/o-problema-ilustrata/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to O problema ilustrata.">O problema ilustrata.</a></h1>                        <div class="date">                                     Friday, 19 August, Year 3 d.Tr.&nbsp;|&nbsp;Author: <a href="http://trilema.com/author/admin/" title="Posts by Mircea Popescu">Mircea Popescu</a>                                                        </div>

                        <div class="entry">
